OL,3,CRed tape could 'jeopardise' Shetland
OL,4,Cspace launch plans, expert warns
OL,6,FPlans to launch rockets into space
OL,7,Ffrom a Scottish island could be
OL,8,Fjeopardised if the UK's licensing
OL,9,Fregime is not fit for purpose, a legal
OL,10,Fexpert has warned.
OL,12,FShetland has the UK's only licensed
OL,13,F"vertical launch" spaceport ` at
OL,14,FSaxaVord on the northernmost inhabited
OL,15,Fisland of Unst.
OL,17,FA number of companies hope to launch
OL,18,Fsatellites from there, with the first
OL,19,Fblast-off expected some time in 2026.
