OL,4,Cspace launch plans, expert warns
OL,6,FHowever, space law expert Alex
OL,7,FSimmonds, from the University of
OL,8,FDundee, has warned that without the
OL,9,Fright regulatory framework, the UK
OL,10,Fspace launch sector could lose out to
OL,11,Fstiff competition from overseas.
OL,13,F"We are dealing with very dangerous
OL,14,Ftechnology," he explained.
OL,16,F"There are lots of safety
OL,17,Fconsiderations that need to be taken
OL,18,Finto account.
