OL,3,CRed tape could 'jeopardise' Shetland
OL,4,Cspace launch plans, expert warns
OL,6,F"Regulators have been very cautious at
OL,7,Fthis stage, which is a good thing, but
OL,8,Fa balance needs to be achieved as
OL,9,Fbusinesses do not like to be caught up
OL,10,Fin red tape.
OL,12,F"If that happens then they may look
OL,13,Felsewhere, which could jeopardise the
OL,14,FUK's involvement before it gets off
OL,15,Fthe ground.
OL,17,F"The fitness and purpose of the UK's
OL,18,Flicensing regime will be integral to
OL,19,Fwhether or not the UK's space
OL,20,Fprogramme can be judged a success or
OL,21,Fnot."
