OL,4,Cspace launch plans, expert warns
OL,6,FDr Simmonds said the UK is currently
OL,7,F"in a very good place" in terms of its
OL,8,Flaws and regulations around space
OL,9,Flaunches.
OL,11,FHowever, he said "more could probably
OL,12,Fbe done" in areas like the regulation
OL,13,Fof space debris, and the impact on
OL,14,FEarth's environment of bringing
OL,15,Fobjects back from space.
OL,17,FDr Simmonds's warning echoes concerns
OL,18,Fraised elsewhere about the risks
OL,19,Ffacing the UK's nascent space launch
OL,20,Fsector.
