OL,4,Cspace launch plans, expert warns
OL,6,FIn September, a report by the Scottish
OL,7,FAffairs Committee warned Scotland
OL,8,Frisks missing a "generational
OL,9,Fopportunity" to become a leader in the
OL,10,Findustry, and called on the UK
OL,11,FGovernment to do more to support it.
OL,13,FThe report's conclusion stated: "It is
OL,14,Fclear that the UK is falling behind
OL,15,Fits European counterparts in terms of
OL,16,Fpublic investment, leaving Scottish
OL,17,Fspaceports at a competitive
OL,18,Fdisadvantage in a fast-moving global
OL,19,Fmarket.
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@LO]uD@aOU
