OL,3,CRed tape could 'jeopardise' Shetland
OL,4,Cspace launch plans, expert warns
OL,6,F"Without sustained backing from the
OL,7,FGovernment ` particularly in
OL,8,Finfrastructure ` Scotland risks
OL,9,Fmissing a generational opportunity to
OL,10,Flead in space launch."
OL,12,FScotland's geographical position far
OL,13,Fnorth of the Equator makes it
OL,14,Fparticularly favourable for what is
OL,15,Fknown as polar synchronous orbits `
OL,16,Fwhere satellites travel over both
OL,17,Fpoles.
