OL,6,FCommercial spaceport activity in the
OL,7,FUK is governed by the Space Industry
OL,8,FAct 2018, supplemented by the Space
OL,9,FIndustry Regulations 2021.
OL,11,FYet as Dr Simmonds pointed out, these
OL,12,Fonly apply to rockets operating above
OL,13,Fthe stratosphere ` the layer of the
OL,14,Fatmosphere roughly 10-50km above the
OL,15,FEarth's surface.
OL,17,F"Some rockets are used for low-level
OL,18,Fpurposes so are not governed by the
OL,19,FSpace Industry Act, but are dealt
OL,20,Fthrough permission from the Civil
OL,21,FAviation Authority," he explained.
