OL,6,F"This means they are not covered by
OL,7,Fthe same environmental checks.
OL,9,F"This is something that either
OL,10,FParliament needs to be mindful of when
OL,11,Fit wants to boast about any success
OL,12,Fthese spaceports generate.
OL,14,F"This being said, the legislature
OL,15,Fclearly has to draw the line
OL,16,Fsomewhere, and this isn't helped by
OL,17,Fthe fact that there is no
OL,18,Finternational agreement on where space
OL,19,Factually does begin."
