OL,6,FDr Simmonds is in no doubt that the
OL,7,Fspace economy will only continue to
OL,8,Fgrow, and Scotland stands to benefit
OL,9,Feconomically from it.
OL,11,FAt the same time, he warned the growth
OL,12,Fin space exploration brings with it a
OL,13,Fnumber of unprecedented challenges for
OL,14,Flegislators.
OL,16,F"Space law is constantly evolving and
OL,17,Fis layered very differently than that
OL,18,Fhere on Earth," he said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@OO]
