OL,3,CRed tape could 'jeopardise' Shetland
OL,4,Cspace launch plans, expert warns
OL,6,F"As we look to the future, we need to
OL,7,Fdiscuss how laws adopted here on Earth
OL,8,Fmay apply elsewhere."
OL,10,FHe gave as an example the fact it
OL,11,Ftakes about 24 minutes to transmit
OL,12,Finformation to Mars ` and longer for
OL,13,Fmore distant objects ` due to the fact
OL,14,Fcommunications can only go as fast as
OL,15,Fthe speed of light.
