OL,4,Cspace launch plans, expert warns
OL,6,F"If a law comes into force on planet
OL,7,FEarth, let's say at midnight Greenwich
OL,8,FMean Time, would that bind astronauts
OL,9,Fwho are 24 minutes away at the speed
OL,10,Fof light, who have got no way of
OL,11,Factually seeing the details of that
OL,12,Finstrument?" he asked.
OL,14,F"Would ignorance of the law be a
OL,15,Fdefence to them?
OL,17,F"There are a lot of exciting and
OL,18,Finteresting areas that are on the
OL,19,Fhorizon with this."
